comments: Morant (MEM) is in the paint for about three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Tillman (MEM) maintains a legal guarding position during the post play at the basket by Jokic (DEN).

During the drive, Campazzo (DEN) maintains his defensive path retreating alongside Morant (MEM) and absorbs the contact. From all available angles Campazzo avoids making contact to Morant's arm on his dislodge attempt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor is overturned to Nuggets possession.
Before the off-ball cut on the perimeter, Barton (DEN) and Melton (MEM) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Barton (DEN) briefly places, before immediately removing, a resting hand from Morant's (MEM) back and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
During the pick, Anderson (MEM) and Dozier (DEN) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Porter Jr. (DEN) briefly grasps and immediately releases Anderson's (MEM) jersey without affecting his FOM.
Morant (MEM) stops his dribble by bringing two hands to the ball and then restarts his dribble.
Jokic (DEN) and Melton (MEM) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal off-ball in the post.
Allen (MEM) extends his arm to deliver contact to Jokic's (DEN) body, which affects his jump shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for about three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.

During the rebound, Tillman (MEM) and Jokic (DEN) mutually engage and disengage and the contact is marginal. Melton (MEM) moves toward the basket and inadvertently makes incidental foot to foot contact with Jokic, which causes Melton to lose his balance.

Replay review of the foul called on Campazzo (DEN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Campazzo maintains a legal guarding position off-ball when Morant (MEM) initiates contact that dislodges him.
Morant (MEM) fumbles the ball as tries to gather the ball by bringing it behind his back. He is able to legally regain possession of the ball and immediately passes it.
Barton (DEN) legally contests Melton's (MEM) fadeaway shot attempt.
Anderson (MEM) is established in a legal guarding position in Barton's (DEN) path and he absorbs the contact created by Barton as he loses control of his dribble on the spin move.
Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact created by Allen (MEM) by collapsing his forearm into his body during the play at the basket.
During the rebound, Tillman (MEM) cleanly tips the ball away from Jokic (DEN) and Campazzo (DEN) is able to toss the ball off of Allen's (MEM) body while he is out of bounds.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling of Nuggets possession is confirmed.
Tillman (MEM) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Jokic (DEN).

Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position with one forearm collapsed against his body and the other arm in a vertical position as he jumps alongside Morant (MEM) to contest his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Morant's (MEM) path and absorbs the contact during the dribble hand-off.

During the inbound, Morant (MEM) and Campazzo (DEN) engage and disengage off ball and the contact is marginal. Campazzo makes marginal contact with his teammate Jokic's (DEN) back as he disengages with Morant.
Harrison (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position on Morant (MEM) at the end of the drive.
Harrison (DEN) jumps for the rebound and incidental contact occurs with Morant's (MEM) body as the game clock expires.
Anderson (MEM) makes contact with Jokic's (DEN) arm and the contact affects his SQBR.
Anderson (MEM) could be deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within about three seconds.
Morant (MEM) goes to and not through Campazzo (DEN) when he releases from the contact by spinning off of him to start his drive to the basket.
Anderson (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in Campazzo's (DEN) path and absorbs the contact.
Porter Jr. (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Morant (MEM).
Jokic (DEN) draws Tillman (MEM) in the air towards him and he makes contact to Jokic's body as he returns to the floor that affects his SQBR.
Porter Jr. (DEN) cleanly deflects the pass away and the ball touches the sideline out of bounds before he can recover it.
Jokic (DEN) places a resting forearm on Morant's (MEM) body and marginal contact occurs as Morant's intended trajectory remains unchanged on his driving shot attempt.
Tillman (MEM) releases his inbounds pass within 5 seconds.
Dozier (DEN) legally contests Allen's (MEM) jump shot attempt.

Anderson (MEM) maintains a legal guarding position on Barton (DEN) when Barton loses control of the ball. Anderson and Jokic (DEN) both make clean ball contact as they tip the ball before Jokic recovers it.
Anderson (MEM) reaches in and any contact that occurs with Jokic (DEN) is marginal.
Anderson (MEM) commits a take foul on Dozier (DEN).
Anderson (MEM) releases his inbounds pass within 5 seconds.
Campazzo (DEN) cleanly deflects the pass away and is able to save the ball before he goes out of bounds.
